        android:text="Thank you for listenting all my bakwas all the time, thank you for drinking chai with me on those calm winter mornings, bs ye kehna k thank u ki list boht lambi hay par tu konsa mar raha :) birthday hi tou hay bs teri. Khayr. Bas zohaib tu ne haarna ni hay aur hmesha himmat jawaan rkhni. I believe in you that you will ace everything you want to. Nothing is impossible for zeb nigga :) "
